{{!--
    Craft section panel — the framed translucent panel + optional gold-gothic
    icon heading shared by every craft-sheet tab (terracraft / aircraft /
    watercraft; one vehicle-sheet family, NOT per-system variants). Body content
    is provided by the caller via {{> @partial-block}}.

    The 7-system accent chain on the heading + icon is kept INLINE here on
    purpose — its migration to `themeClassFor` is tracked separately (#422); this
    partial only de-duplicates the STRUCTURE, not the colour tokens.

    Block-partial usage:
        {{#> systems/wh40k-rpg/templates/actor/partial/craft-section.hbs
             icon="fa-tachometer-alt" titleKey="WH40K.Vehicle.Statistics"}}
            ... body markup ...
        {{/systems/wh40k-rpg/templates/actor/partial/craft-section.hbs}}

    Hash arguments:
        titleKey — i18n key for the heading. When omitted, no heading renders
                   (the panel is just the framed body).
        icon     — Font Awesome class (e.g. "fa-tachometer-alt"). Optional; only
                   meaningful when titleKey is present.
--}}
<div class="tw-bg-[rgba(40,35,30,0.7)] tw-border tw-border-[#444] tw-rounded-[6px] tw-p-4 tw-mb-4">
    {{#if titleKey}}
    <h3 class="tw-text-[1.1rem] tw-font-bold tw-text-gold {{themeClassFor 'accent'}} tw-mb-2 tw-flex tw-items-center tw-gap-2">
        {{#if icon}}<i class="fas {{icon}} tw-text-gold {{themeClassFor 'accent'}}"></i> {{/if}}{{localize titleKey}}
    </h3>
    {{/if}}
    {{> @partial-block}}
</div>
